OL,3,CConcerns over two doctors sees 20
OL,4,Cpatient deaths referred to Coroner
OL,6,FThere are concerns that the deaths of
OL,7,Fat least 20 rheumatology patients in
OL,8,FJersey were caused directly or
OL,9,Findirectly by their care in the
OL,10,Fisland's health service.
OL,12,FThe cases have been referred to the
OL,13,Fisland's Coroner for new inquests
OL,14,Fwhich will be carried out by the
OL,15,FViscount, relatives are being informed
OL,16,Fof the development by Health and
OL,17,FCommunity Services (HCS) over the
OL,18,Fphone.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
