OL,4,Cpatient deaths referred to Coroner
OL,6,FFamily members will also have the
OL,7,Fopportunity to meet the Chief of
OL,8,FService, a Consultant Rheumatologist
OL,9,Fand a well-being expert with follow-up
OL,10,Fsupport offered where needed.
OL,12,FThese cases are part of an ongoing
OL,13,Fclinical audit into 190 patients who
OL,14,Fwere in Jersey's Rheumatology Service
OL,15,Funder the care of 'Dr Y' and 'Dr Z'
OL,16,Fand have died since January 2019.
