OL,6,FJust over 120 have been reviewed so
OL,7,Ffar while HCS Medical Director Patrick
OL,8,FArmstrong believes "probably between
OL,9,F40 and 50" will be referred to the
OL,10,FViscount and has called the situation
OL,11,Fa "scandal".
OL,13,FHe adds: "This is the most difficult
OL,14,Fand challenging situation I've had to
OL,15,Fface in my 33-year career as a doctor.
