OL,6,F"I am the one that requested this
OL,7,Freview by The Royal College of
OL,8,FPhysicians, the first time issues were
OL,9,Fraised to me by a junior doctor I
OL,10,Facted upon and this is where it's led
OL,11,Fto.
OL,13,F"We can only say sorry, this is a
OL,14,Fproblem that's been going on for a
OL,15,Fvery long time and came to light two
OL,16,Fand a half years ago."
OL,18,F'Dr Y' is still on the payroll but not
OL,19,Fcurrently practising in Jersey while
OL,20,F'Dr Z' left the island some time ago.
