OL,4,Cpatient deaths referred to Coroner
OL,6,FMr Armstrong says assessments by
OL,7,Findependent specialists have so far
OL,8,Frevealed that 33 living patients may
OL,9,Fhave been harmed by their diagnosis,
OL,10,Ftreatment and care under these two
OL,11,Fdoctors.
OL,13,FThey have been given an apology and
OL,14,Fcompensation will be offered, he hopes
OL,15,Flater this year, either on a case-by-
OL,16,Fcase basis or through a general scheme.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
