OL,3,CConcerns over two doctors sees 20
OL,4,Cpatient deaths referred to Coroner
OL,6,FIt follows a damning independent
OL,7,Freport published earlier this year
OL,8,Fwhich found that the standard of
OL,9,Frheumatology care in Jersey was "well
OL,10,Fbelow what the review team would
OL,11,Fconsider acceptable".
OL,13,FAt the time, HCS admitted it is
OL,14,F"inevitable" that some patients "will
OL,15,Fhave been harmed clinically,
OL,16,Femotionally or economically by their
OL,17,Fearlier diagnosis or treatment".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
