OL,6,FThe investigation by the Royal College
OL,7,Fof Physicians had been triggered by
OL,8,Fconcerns from locum doctors over
OL,9,Frecord-keeping, case management and
OL,10,Fcommunication.
OL,12,FMr Armstrong adds: "I would like to
OL,13,Freassure patients of the Rheumatology
OL,14,FService that the recommendations made
OL,15,Fby the Royal College for improvements
OL,16,Fto the services are progressing well.
OL,18,F"Of the 26 recommendations made, 16
OL,19,Fhave been fully implemented and the
OL,20,Fremaining 10 are well on the way to
OL,21,Fbeing implemented."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
